data.description: Built by Taylor Morrison, this home boasts a very spacious Floorplan consisting of  5 OVERSIZED bedroom's, ALL with walk in closets, stunning 2 story living space, high ceilings, Lovely island kitchen with a DOUBLE PANTRY and open to the family room.  Large home office, formal living and formal dining. Large Gameroom and Media room with surround sound. The home has been meticulously maintained, it's a blank canvas ready to be tailored to your family needs, very private backyard with space for a pool, large covered patio with 2 ceiling fans.  Incredible RARE feature is the ENORMOUS GARAGE, equivalent to that of a 4 car garage, perfect for the family needing storage or a workshop. Smart Technology, & On-Demand Tankless Water Heater! The community is Surrounded by trees and nature reserve. Minutes away from Grand Parkway & Interstate 45, the property is located near Bush Airport, ExxonMobil, HP, St. Luke Medical Center, Houston Methodist Medical Center, and The Woodlands Mall.
